  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Let's make Anurav PM: Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe said that if JVP leader Anura Kumara's program succeeds, he will be appointed as Prime Minister and I will resign from the post of Prime Minister. Ministers will also resign, he said.",
        "We have presented programs. Help take it forward, no need to take to the streets. He said that we will convene the Parliament on the coming Thursday and Friday, hold a discussion and take forward the work plans."
      ],
